1. Kompanija je nedavno preuzela* novu fabriku u Kini. (The company recently took over a new factory in China.)
2. Oni su preuzeli* odgovornost za organizovanje događaja. (They have taken responsibility for organizing the event.)
3. Vlada je preuzela* mere za suzbijanje korupcije. (The government has taken measures to combat corruption.)
4. Novi direktor je nedavno preuzeo* rukovođenje timom. (The new director recently took over the management of the team.)
5. Nakon ostavke, ministarstvo je privremeno preuzelo* vođenje te agencije. (After the resignation, the ministry temporarily took over the management of the agency.)
6. Nisam siguran ko će preuzeti* tvoj posao dok si na odmoru. (I'm not sure who will take over your job while you're on vacation.)
7. Da li si preuzeo* dokumente koje sam ti ostavio? (Did you take the documents I left for you?)
8. Očekujemo da će se nova vlada uskoro preuzeti* dužnost. (We expect the new government to take office soon.)
9. Kompanija je preuzela* vodeću poziciju na tržištu. (The company has taken the leading position in the market.)
10. Naše preduzeće je preuzelo* nekoliko manjih firmi u poslednjih nekoliko godina. (Our company has taken over several smaller firms in the last few years.)